com.energyxxer.commodore.functionlogic.selector

Class Selector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.energyxxer.commodore.functionlogic.selector.Selector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Entity, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Selector
extends java.lang.Object
implements Entity, java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents an entity selector used in-game to target any number of entities, using a mix of base selectors and arguments.
    See Also:
    Entity
